      <title>非洲洪水肆虐 5500 万人面临饥饿</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/floods-across-nigeria-mali-niger-hit-millions-battling-hunger-in-africa</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西非和中非大片地区遭遇了几十年来最严重的洪灾，加剧了该地区创纪录的粮食危机，联合国称该地区已有 5500 万人陷入饥饿。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/floods-across-nigeria-mali-niger-hit-millions-battling-hunger-in-africa</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 08:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列在战争“新阶段”扩大对真主党的打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/israel-widens-strikes-against-hezbollah-in-new-phase-of-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列宣布对黎巴嫩南部地区武装组织真主党的战争进入“新阶段”，并进一步升级敌对行动，周四对黎巴嫩南部地区实施了大规模空袭。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/israel-widens-strikes-against-hezbollah-in-new-phase-of-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 07:27:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国 8 月零售销售好于预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/uk-retail-sales-beat-expectations-during-sunny-spell-in-august</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于消费者渴望享受晴朗天气和夏季折扣，抵消了日益加剧的政治和财政忧虑，英国八月份零售额加速增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/uk-retail-sales-beat-expectations-during-sunny-spell-in-august</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 06:10:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
